Package: ecreml
Title: Incorporates ECs into the analysis of agricultural trial data containing GxExM interactions
Version: 0.1.001
Authors@R: 
    person("Michael", "Mumford", , "Michael.Mumford@dpi.qld.gov.au", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5037-8680"))
Description: This R-package complements the statistical methodology outlined in Mumford et al. (2023) 
	that enables environmental covariates (ECs) to be incorporated into the multi-environment trial (MET) analysis
	of agricultural consisting of Genotype x Environment x Management (GxExM) interaction effects. Specifically, 
	this R-package contains a suite of functions that automate the process of identifying key ECs contributing to the
	GxExM interaction after a baseline model is fitted using the ASReml R-package that does not contain any EC information.
